Join us here for a PREVIEW of our daily one-hour RUMBLE show. 
To continue watching the show in full, join me exclusively over on RUMBLE: https://bit.ly/SF546-live

Today, I’m talking with Dr. Aseem Malhotra, a cardiologist who went from mainstream medical insider to one of the most outspoken critics of Big Pharma and the COVID narrative. We dive into the corruption that shaped pandemic policies, the vaccine rollout, and the broader crisis in healthcare—where corporate interests have taken precedence over public well-being. Aseem shares the personal tragedy that led him to question the system and explains why figures like RFK Jr. and Jay Bhattacharya are now in positions to drive real change. We also explore the deeper spiritual and societal implications of this bat
title: They Lied to Us – The Vaccine, Big Pharma & Global Corruption with Dr. Aseem Malhotra – SF546
